com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.receivers

Class CreateReceiverRequestExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.RequestExecutor<Receiver>
      • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.executor.receivers.CreateReceiverRequestExecutor

  • public class CreateReceiverRequestExecutor
extends RequestExecutor<Receiver>
    Request executor provided by ReceiversApi. Use this class if you want to create receivers through fluent API in chained fashion, for example: 
       
   KontaktCloud kontaktCloud = KontaktCloudFactory.create();
   kontaktCloud.receivers().create(receiver).execute();
